@page "/privacy"

<PageTitle>PickJSON - Privacy</PageTitle>

<div class="page">
  <div class="w-full px-5 md:px-50 py-12 text-white overflow-y-scroll">

    <div class="flex space-x-5 mb-6 items-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-light">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Last updated: 14 February 2026</p>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>PickJSON</strong> ("we", "us", "our") handles information when you use
      <a href="https://www.pickjson.com" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500" target="_blank"
         rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.pickjson.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">1. Data We Process</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      PickJSON is a browser-based developer tool. We do not require user accounts. JSON you paste into the tool is
      processed in your browser and is not intentionally stored by us on our servers.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      When you visit our website, the following data may be processed by us and/or our third-party ad vendor:
    </p>

    <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li>IP address</li>
      <li>Browser and device information</li>
      <li>Approximate geolocation inferred from IP</li>
      <li>Page visits, ad interactions, and related technical signals</li>
      <li>Cookie and similar identifier data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">2. Advertising and Third-Party Cookies</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      We use <strong>Monetag</strong> to serve ads on parts of this website.
      Third-party advertisers may place cookies (or similar technologies) in your browser to deliver ads, cap frequency,
      and measure campaign performance.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      You can manage cookies using your browser settings. Blocking some cookies may affect how ads or some site features
      work.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      This disclosure is provided in line with Monetag publisher terms requiring a publicly available privacy policy and
      cookie disclosure for end users.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">3. Legal Basis (EU/EEA)</h2>

    <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li><strong>Consent:</strong> advertising cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
      <li><strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> security, core website operation, and fraud prevention</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">4. Opt-Out and Consent Withdrawal</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      You may withdraw or change consent at any time by updating browser cookie settings and local storage.
      For Monetag ad personalization controls, you can also use Monetag's opt-out page:
      <a href="https://monetag.com/opt-out/" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500" target="_blank"
         rel="noopener noreferrer">https://monetag.com/opt-out/</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      If push notifications are enabled by a third-party ad flow, unsubscribe through your browser/device notification
      settings and Monetag guidance.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">5. Third-Party Policies</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      For details on how Monetag handles data, see:
    </p>

    <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li>
        Monetag Privacy Policy:
        <a href="https://monetag.com/privacy/" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500" target="_blank"
           rel="noopener noreferrer">https://monetag.com/privacy/</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        Monetag Cookies Policy:
        <a href="https://monetag.com/cookies-policy/" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500"
           target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://monetag.com/cookies-policy/</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        Monetag Terms:
        <a href="https://monetag.com/terms/" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500" target="_blank"
           rel="noopener noreferrer">https://monetag.com/terms/</a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">6. Data Protection Rights</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict personal data
      processing, and to object to certain processing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>

    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      We may update this policy from time to time. Changes are posted on this page with a revised date.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 mb-3 text-xl font-light">8. Contact</h2>

    <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
      For privacy questions about PickJSON:
      <a href="mailto:pickjson@outlook.com" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500">pickjson@outlook.com</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</div>
